The main changes are in [cli/src/github.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/src/github.rs), [cli/src/state.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/src/state.rs), [cli/src/app.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/src/app.rs), [cli/src/tui.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/src/tui.rs), and the default template files [cli/templates/default/state-machine.yml](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/templates/default/state-machine.yml) and [cli/templates/default/agents.yml](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/templates/default/agents.yml). The feature now models normalized GitHub PR evidence for draft state, review state, checks, and mergeability; supports `passing` / `failing` / `pending` / `manual` built-in evidence; wires those into grouped gates; persists the snapshot shape in feature state; and renders the evidence in both status output and the TUI. Tests were updated in [cli/tests/github.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/tests/github.rs), [cli/tests/state.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/tests/state.rs), [cli/tests/app.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/tests/app.rs), and [cli/tests/tui.rs](/tmp/calypso-worktrees/feat-cli-github-gate-evaluators/cli/tests/tui.rs).

